      <title>泰晤士水务公司债权人质疑30亿英镑救助贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/thames-water-set-for-pivotal-hearing-on-3-billion-rescue-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表泰晤士水务公司竞争对手的律师周二向伦敦一位法官表示，泰晤士水务公司计划获得的 30 亿英镑（38 亿美元）救助贷款将向该公司“索要赎金”，并将控制权移交给优先债权人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/thames-water-set-for-pivotal-hearing-on-3-billion-rescue-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
